==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unmuffle
<hw>Un*muf"fle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>muffle</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To take a covering from, as the face; to
uncover.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To remove the muffling of, as a drum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unmutable</ent>⟦br⟧
